{"tid":2432796,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"發左個股災惡夢","createTime":"2021-03-04T14:23:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T14:30:20.000Z","uid":286928,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4b11910ab9dcf21422234a0f81c5920cea679129","tid":2432796,"uid":286928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T14:23:01.000Z","msg":"3月5日，陳茂波宣佈將對香港居民徵收20%資產增值税，該法案預期會在同年10月三讀通過。該消息發佈後恆指應聲下跌，收市時恆指暴跌8.6%，科技指數下跌15%，部分H股所對應的A股因此跌停板。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n受加息預期及香港資產增值税拖累，納指單日暴跌10%，創2020年3月以來單日最大跌幅，而SP500 僅下跌3.3%，故未有觸發熔斷機制。Robinhood宣佈暫停所有期權買賣並發行20億美元債券。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2536e98aa5f88e27eb03aa4fa7c4697a464f0988","tid":2432796,"uid":156652,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T14:24:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pdDgVvY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpdDgVvY.gif&h=2f199d94&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42d994ccf9ca6bdd9636dbbba176d521139c0c88","tid":2432796,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T14:28:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a5953fc9f7338bd257d2263c0c7edeb9f5a3e7","tid":2432796,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T14:29:00.000Z","msg":"樓價呢？"},{"pid":"61f3f9705a35c5017f88c1ba2f3a43c1bec0d749","tid":2432796,"uid":17721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T14:30:20.000Z","msg":"受加息預期及香港資產增值税拖累，納指單日暴跌10%<br />\n呢句有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" clas